---
description: Project coding standards
globs: "**/*.py"
---
- Use Python 3.10 features only; avoid 3.11-specific syntax
- Pip and virtualenv for dependencies, no Poetry or Docker builds
- Prefer subprocess.run over os.system
- Include type hints and Google-style docstrings
- Keep code simple and reuse scripts in `scripts/`
- Format with Black and isort
